{"tid":2248821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣覺得依家過緊既正常生活都好似偷返黎咁...好大罪疚感","createTime":"2020-10-19T01:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T02:10:30.000Z","uid":41411,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50248aa7f721946fb4a04488fb5a438fdab5d4fa","tid":2248821,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"抗爭無晒聲氣...大家都好似回歸左所謂既正常生活咁<br />\n但我自己每一次同朋友嘻嘻哈哈既時候就會自動諗起一班被扣押緊...被告緊...或者已經坐緊監既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就會即刻無左果種歡愉既心情 個人覺得好有罪疚感...佢地面對住極權既審判；而我就係度吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一方面又唔知可以點幫到佢地 (自己有keep住課612...但好似得返好少人課金咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家都養成習慣做課金師..好多手足都係靠緊612幫手)<br />\n<br />\n9UP廢文 大家可以唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW <span class=\"x-large\"><strong>#SAVE12HKYOUTHS</strong></span>"},{"pid":"41b5f3c507ddbe180f9a4449589408beb6c576f2","tid":2248821,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbedd5d127862b3026834d153a8fae784bcf9675","tid":2248821,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be87615368439875a83c4672b3e9750caa4e6919","tid":2248821,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"大家都明，但我相信出事既手足會希望你哋每日都過得開心<br />\n人生好寶貴，好好珍惜每日唔好浪費時間同人嘈無謂野"}]}